com.activityscheduler.domain

Class ActivitySchedule

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.activityscheduler.domain.AbstractDomainObject
      • com.activityscheduler.domain.ActivitySchedule
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class ActivitySchedule
extends AbstractDomainObject
    A domain class extending AbstractDomainObject to hold the activity schedule information for an event

    This class consist of following domain driven design method

    • addTeam() - Add a team to the schedule.
    • getTeamCount() - Get the count of teams in the schedule
    • printSchedule() - Print the schedule in human readable format
    Author:
    rbutti
